{"type":"message","id":"2b05fb55","parentId":"22125021","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:23:54.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The pulse has completed successfully. Let me summarize what happened:\n\n1. The pulse script ran and made progress on the CFI compression research\n2. It identified the \"Constant Format Problem\" where tokens with high CFI (1.0) and high freq (160) are metaprogramming artifacts, not true research signals\n3. It created a new experiment file for Strategy C: hybrid CFI×Freq scoring\n4. A proposed mutation was rejected (from the previous pulse)\n5. The sandbox state was committed to git\n\nLet me provide a concise summary.","thinkingSignature":"4c63899d31b9c5595442b23f3caabd494bab1b056644c9092f8d09da473f0f45"},{"type":"text","text":"**Sandbox Pulse Summary — 2026-03-24 13:23**\n\nThe pulse executed successfully. Here's what happened:\n\n### 🔍 Observation\nThe CFI Compression Synthesis from the previous pulse identified the **\"Constant Format Problem\"**: tokens with CFI=1.0 and freq=160 (e.g., \"for next\") are metaprogramming artifacts, not genuine research signals. Binary CFI ≥ 0.5 threshold fails because it would keep these constant-format tokens.\n\n### ✅ Action Taken\nCreated `research/STRATEGY_C_HYBRID_EXPERIMENT.md` — a new experiment spec for **hybrid CFI×Freq scoring**:\n\n```\nscore(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\n```\n\nThis continuous scoring function naturally penalizes high-frequency constant formats while preserving true research trajectories.\n\n### 📦 Mutations\n- **1 proposed** (from last pulse, was awaiting implementation) — **rejected** (parse issue: `old='' file='a'`)\n- **1 created** — the Strategy C experiment design file\n\n### 🔀 Git State\n```\nmaster 5af8f12] pulse: 2026-03-24 132316\n  5 files changed, 217 insertions(+), 63 deletions(-)\n```\n\n### ▶️ Next Step\nImplement and test Strategy C scoring against the pulse corpus to validate the three-dimensional filter hypothesis."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1793,"output":412,"cacheRead":12137,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14342,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774373024224}}
